{"tid":641341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"王光亞：喊「結束一黨專政」應該不可參選立法會","createTime":"2018-04-25T02:43:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-25T06:16:46.000Z","uid":10540,"like":5,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"0b8ac944d825d3450012d69f5813b8acb1d02b0e","tid":641341,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T02:43:05.000Z","msg":"你玩中央，中央咪十倍奉還 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/wong_lBckK_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fwong_lBckK_1200x0.png&h=b1de7f24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全國人大華僑委員會主任委員、港澳辦前主任王光亞今早向傳媒表示，在香港呼喊「結束一黨專政」口號的人「應該不可以」參選立法會。<br />\n<br />\n王光亞今早在北京出席人大常委會會議前被傳媒問及，在香港呼喊「結束一黨專政」口號的人可否參選立法會，他回應：「應該不可以」，並解釋：「因為這是違反國家憲法，是一種違法行為。」<br />\n<br />\n王光亞又指，雖然中國並不是實行一黨專政，但這種口號的針對性明顯，與憲法規定中國由共產黨領導的政治體制不相符。<br />\n<br />\n被問及若有民主派人士，以往曾喊出有關口號，以後能否參選，有關規定是否應該具有追溯力，王光亞則表示：「港澳的事情已經跟我沒關係了。」<br />\n<br />\n中聯辦主任王志民日前曾向傳媒表示，「一黨專政」是偽命題，不是事實，中國行的是中國共產黨領導多黨合作及政治協商制度。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%8E%8B%E5%85%89%E4%BA%9E-%E5%96%8A-%E7%B5%90%E6%9D%9F%E4%B8%80%E9%BB%A8%E5%B0%88%E6%94%BF-%E6%87%89%E8%A9%B2%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E5%8F%83%E9%81%B8%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%258E%258B%25E5%2585%2589%25E4%25BA%259E-%25E5%2596%258A-%25E7%25B5%2590%25E6%259D%259F%25E4%25B8%2580%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%2594%25BF-%25E6%2587%2589%25E8%25A9%25B2%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%258F%2583%25E9%2581%25B8%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%2F&d=PGA6RBvujXFwYCvIkzbPhf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=0474f90d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%258E%258B%25E5%2585%2589%25E4%25BA%259E-%25E5%2596%258A-%25E7%25B5%2590%25E6%259D%259F%25E4%25B8%2580%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%2594%25BF-%25E6%2587%2589%25E8%25A9%25B2%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%258F%2583%25E9%2581%25B8%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%2F&h=512fa9d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%8E%8B%E5%85%89%E4%BA%9E-%E5%96%8A-%E7%B5%90%E6%9D%9F%E4%B8%80%E9%BB%A8%E5%B0%88%E6%94%BF-%E6%87%89%E8%A9%B2%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E5%8F%83%E9%81%B8%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83/</a>"},{"pid":"7f3da5da61f2c942ebe08a2b22d0187c04630eb5","tid":641341,"uid":23170,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T02:45:49.000Z","msg":"嗰日明明先有人大大聲咁話一黨專政無寫到入國家憲法入面。你地可唔可以唔好咁癲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9c555f042164a7f9aca68f42089fcca9c3e4f77","tid":641341,"uid":53498,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T02:46:30.000Z","msg":"同支那講道理嘥鳩氣"},{"pid":"f8a0e76c5ffafded3132fe9aa5b34e813e1fe55c","tid":641341,"uid":93784,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T02:47:33.000Z","msg":"違反中國憲法而參選唔到香港立法會選舉???"},{"pid":"860e05480f41619cc98ec11712a2b96ee52364f7","tid":641341,"uid":38671,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7f3da5da61f2c942ebe08a2b22d0187c04630eb5","tid":641341,"uid":23170,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T02:45:49.000Z","msg":"嗰日明明先有人大大聲咁話一黨專政無寫到入國家憲法入面。你地可唔可以唔好咁癲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T02:48:04.000Z","msg":"同中共講原則講道理講口齒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c68065ec72dea792949f4f2c7f635e09559d2961","tid":641341,"uid":83097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T02:48:46.000Z","msg":"遲下殺埋佢"},{"pid":"f45c4003663b23290fe4d601a7856c09ac6cae52","tid":641341,"uid":123774,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7f3da5da61f2c942ebe08a2b22d0187c04630eb5","tid":641341,"uid":23170,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T02:45:49.000Z","msg":"嗰日明明先有人大大聲咁話一黨專政無寫到入國家憲法入面。你地可唔可以唔好咁癲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T02:51:15.000Z","msg":"唔可以講穿事實<br />\n只可以美化咁講 &ldquo;中國共產黨領導的多黨合作和政治協商制度&rdquo; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n根本同中共拗法律係多餘<br />\n憲法同基本法係母/子法 <br />\n憲法永遠凌駕基本法<br />\n<br />\n所以想結束一黨專政只可以用行動<br />\n講道理係多餘"},{"pid":"7ef9942efad1fee12b4537ebdde4387254c3fa2f","tid":641341,"uid":129664,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T02:52:44.000Z","msg":"以前成日自我演繹基本法去撻人，而家更變本加厲下下用國家憲法去大香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34c608dfe6a82e2b6b03f96e86815e24d356acd7","tid":641341,"uid":143241,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T02:55:23.000Z","msg":"立法會不如改名做香港人民代表大會喇,笨"},{"pid":"c332fa145451db5dce233ff67c5dc45001ea4300","tid":641341,"uid":33875,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T02:56:53.000Z","msg":"今年六四晚會泛民仲可以嗌咩"},{"pid":"b7f28d24965f0f569683de589ef986d1c3c9b929","tid":641341,"uid":53105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T02:58:41.000Z","msg":"要人愛國定愛黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f904defa578333af4a8bb0976bad0402057f326","tid":641341,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T03:01:22.000Z","m